<!-- BEGIN LARAVEL-DDD-TOOLKIT -->

## Laravel DDD Toolkit

This project uses Laravel DDD Toolkit.

Architecture defaults:

- vertical modules under `app/Modules`;
- hexagonal architecture by default;
- pragmatic tactical DDD;
- `make:module`, not `make:domain`;
- ports live in `Application/Ports/In` and `Application/Ports/Out`;
- adapters live in `Infrastructure`;
- Domain must not depend on Laravel, Eloquent, HTTP, Jobs, Infrastructure or external SDKs;
- Application must not depend on Controllers, Requests, Eloquent models or Infrastructure adapters;
- Infrastructure may depend on Application and Domain;
- Eloquent is allowed in Infrastructure;
- repositories are optional and should only be generated when they add value.

Recommended command before finishing architectural changes:

```bash
php artisan ddd:check
```

<!-- END LARAVEL-DDD-TOOLKIT -->
